<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - OrbitBot</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap');
        :root { --primary: #00d2ff; --bg: #09090b; --card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: var(--bg); color: #fff; margin: 0; padding: 40px 20px; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; background: var(--card-bg); padding: 40px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--glass-border); }
        h1 { color: var(--primary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border); padding-bottom: 20px; }
        h2 { margin-top: 30px; color: #e0e0e0; }
        p { color: #aaa; }
        a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; }
        .back-link { display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #888; }
        .back-link:hover { color: #fff; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="back-link"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Home</a>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Last updated: November 16, 2025</p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>OrbitBot collects the minimum amount of data necessary to function:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Server IDs:</strong> To store server-specific settings (if applicable).</li>
            <li><strong>User IDs:</strong> To execute commands requested by specific users.</li>
            <li><strong>Command Usage Logs:</strong> Used temporarily for debugging and analytics, as seen in the Admin Panel.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>Data is used solely for the operation and improvement of OrbitBot. We do not sell or share your data with third parties.</p>

        <h2>3. Data Storage</h2>
        <p>Data is stored securely. Logs are rotated regularly and not kept permanently.</p>

        <h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to request the deletion of any data associated with your Discord User ID. Contact the developer via the support server.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
